ince this is combinational logic, using `always @(*)` is preferred over explicit sensitivity lists.\n*   Initialize output signals (`next_state` and `out`) to zero at the start of the `always` block to guarantee that the block describes pure combinational logic and avoids unintentional latch inference.",
